snippet.title: Why Amber Heard WON'T have a future as an ACTRESS!
snippet.description:
Lately there has been a lot of talk regarding Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. 
With all the evidence against Amber, it is tough to imagine her to have a future as an actress! Johnny got released from his roles without any real evidence, so if she gets convicted there is a big chance that her career will see an end quick. 
We will be going over why exactly we believe this is the case and show you the rumours. 

Let us know if you liked the video and make sure to subscribe to stay up to date :)
